
Overview of noun allotment

The noun allotment has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (44) allotment, allocation -- (a share set aside for a specific purpose)
2. (1) allotment, apportionment, apportioning, allocation, parceling, parcelling, assignation -- (the act of distributing by allotting or apportioning; distribution according to a plan; "the apportionment of seats in the House of Representatives is based on the relative population of each state")
